Package org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RobotCoreGamepadManager
    RobotCoreGamepadManager defines the public interface to the gamepad manager that is available to the RobotCore module.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorListPreference
    ColorListPreference is an enhancement to ListPreference that allows more than just mere strings to be displayed as entries.
    ColorListPreferenceLineItem
    A utility for use with ColorListPreference
    FilledPolygonDrawable
    FilledPolygonDrawable is a simple utility that draws a filled (regular) polygon in a designated color.
    InputManager
    InputManager provides additional access to android.hardware.input.InputManager by unhiding some of its methods.
    LocalByRefIntentExtraHolder
    LocalByRefIntentExtraHolder can be used to pass an object reference by reference into a newly launched activity.
    LocalByRefRequestCodeHolder<T>
    LocalByRefRequestCodeHolder is intended to allow context to be passed from startActivityForResult() to it's subsequent onActivityResult() by way of information keyed by its (dynamic) request code.
    PaintedPathDrawable
    PaintedPathDrawable is a helper class for implementing a Drawable that uses a Paint to draw a Path
    ProgressParameters
    ProgressParameters is a utility class for passing information regarding progress towards completing a task.
    ThemedActivity
    ThemedActivity supports the dynamic theming of activities, even on API 19
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GamepadUser
    A *typed* integer so that we can more easily keep track of things
    UILocation
    UILocation controls whether user interface actions are displayed only locally or also remotely
